<section class="page-margin contained">
    <span class="small-text-16 mono eyebrow">Process</span>
    <h2 id="wireframing">Sketching the interface</h2>
    <p>With a concept in mind, I drew out some ideas for a simple app. Because this is meant to help Lilah remember which artists she likes, listing them out front and center seemed the most appropriate for the main screen.</p>
    <p>Since Lilah also enjoys going to the concerts during the festival, it made sense to include a master schedule of all the events, so she and her friends can keep track of what’s happening in real time and set up alerts for anything she wants to see.</p>
</section>

